---
title: Home
layout: layouts/base.njk
seo:
  title: "Developer Roadmaps"
  description: "Community driven roadmaps, articles and guides for developers to grow in their career."
sitemap:
  priority: 1
  changefreq: monthly
tags:
  - main-sitemap
---

<div class='pb-16'>
  <div class='border-b'>
    <div class='py-16 max-w-[800px] mx-auto container text-center'>
      <h1
        class='text-4xl mb-4 font-bold'>
        Developer Roadmaps</h1>
      <p class='text-gray-500 text-lg'><span class='font-medium text-black'>roadmap.sh</span> is a community effort to
        create
        roadmaps, guides and other
        educational content to help guide the developers in picking up the path and guide their learnings.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='py-12 border-b bg-gray-50 relative'>
    <div class='max-w-[800px] mx-auto container'>
      <h2 class='absolute rounded-lg -top-[17px] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white py-1 px-3 border text-md text-stone-900 font-medium'>Role based Roadmaps</h2>
      <ul class='grid grid-cols-3 gap-2'>
        {% for roadmap in collections['roleRoadmaps'] %}
          <li>
            <a
              class='bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-200 to-teal-200 hover:bg-gray-300 p-3.5 block no-underline rounded-lg'
              href='{{ roadmap.data.permalink }}'
            >
              <span class='block text-black font-regular text-lgmd'>{{ roadmap.data.featuredTitle }}</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='py-12 border-b bg-gray-50 relative'>
    <div class='max-w-[800px] mx-auto container'>
      <h2 class='absolute rounded-lg -top-[17px] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white py-1 px-3 border text-md text-stone-900 font-medium'>Skill based Roadmaps</h2>
      <ul class='grid grid-cols-3 gap-2'>
        {% for roadmap in collections['skillRoadmaps'] %}
          <li>
            <a
              class='bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-200 to-teal-200 hover:bg-gray-300 p-3.5 block no-underline rounded-lg'
              href='{{ roadmap.data.permalink }}'
            >
              <span class='block text-black font-regular text-lgmd'>{{ roadmap.data.featuredTitle }}</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='p-1 container mx-auto max-w-[800px]'>
  <div class='my-8'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl mb-1 font-bold'>Videos</h1>
    <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-1'>
      {% for video in (collections['video'] | reverse).slice(0, 10) %}
        <li>
          <a class='no-underline text-gray-600 hover:text-red-700 flex justify-between' href={{ video.data.page.url }}>
            {{ video.data.title }} <span class='capitalize text-gray-600'>{{ video.data.duration }}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <a href='/videos' class='p-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300'>All Videos</a>
  </div>

  <div class='my-8'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl mb-1 font-bold'>Guides</h1>
    <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-1'>
      {% for guide in (collections['guide'] | reverse).slice(0, 10) %}
        <li>
          <a class='no-underline text-gray-600 hover:text-red-700 flex justify-between' href={{ guide.data.page.url }}>
            {{ guide.data.title }} <span class='capitalize text-gray-600'>{{ guide.data.type }}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <a href='/guides' class='p-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300'>All Guides</a>
  </div>
</div>
